WEBVTT

00:00:00.040 --> 00:00:14.740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

00:01:40.000 --> 00:01:40.720
Sent.

00:01:41.160 --> 00:01:42.240
Let's go save them.

00:01:42.520 --> 00:01:43.479
Leave this to us.

00:01:43.640 --> 00:01:44.370
You go first.

00:01:44.400 --> 00:01:44.920
No.

00:01:45.000 --> 00:01:46.060
Hurry up and leave.

00:01:46.280 --> 00:01:47.520
No. If we leave, we leave together.

00:01:47.520 --> 00:01:48.320
Listen to me.

00:01:48.400 --> 00:01:50.039
We can't leave anything here for the Japanese.

00:01:50.039 --> 00:01:50.770
You go first.

00:01:50.880 --> 00:01:51.920
We'll be right behind you.

00:01:51.920 --> 00:01:52.320
But...

00:01:52.400 --> 00:01:52.880
Go!

00:01:55.880 --> 00:01:56.360
Go!

00:01:56.360 --> 00:01:57.120
Be careful.

00:02:17.160 --> 00:02:17.840
Go!

00:02:40.960 --> 00:02:42.240
Bastards!

00:02:42.520 --> 00:02:44.079
You won't get anything.

00:02:44.200 --> 00:02:45.440
Shoot him!

00:04:02.480 --> 00:04:03.080
Come here.

00:04:05.680 --> 00:04:06.280
Go.

00:04:07.800 --> 00:04:08.800
Captain Matsuda.

00:04:09.120 --> 00:04:12.120
The underground party members upstairs are all dead.

00:04:12.400 --> 00:04:14.520
What is this old lady doing here?

00:04:15.320 --> 00:04:17.040
I'm asking you. What are you doing?

00:04:17.040 --> 00:04:18.360
Do you have any accomplices?

00:04:18.360 --> 00:04:20.040
What are their names? Where are they?

00:04:20.040 --> 00:04:20.720
Speak!

00:04:24.080 --> 00:04:25.210
Section Chief Qian.

00:04:25.320 --> 00:04:26.760
It seems this old lady...

00:04:27.080 --> 00:04:28.480
doesn't understand you.

00:04:30.400 --> 00:04:31.800
Are you mute?

00:04:32.200 --> 00:04:33.200
Speak up quickly.

00:04:33.200 --> 00:04:34.520
Or I'll shoot you dead.

00:04:36.560 --> 00:04:38.000
Child.

00:04:39.280 --> 00:04:40.680
His father.

00:04:42.280 --> 00:04:45.560
The sound of radio waves

00:04:46.800 --> 00:04:49.000
is so beautiful.

00:04:55.320 --> 00:04:56.720
I know.

00:04:58.360 --> 00:05:01.560
That's our son's soul speaking.

00:05:03.320 --> 00:05:05.240
Our son is saying...

00:05:08.200 --> 00:05:09.360
The Japanese...

00:05:10.200 --> 00:05:11.400
won't last long.

00:05:12.720 --> 00:05:13.840
Won't last long.

00:05:14.960 --> 00:05:16.640
Won't last long.

00:05:57.200 --> 00:05:57.920
Sister Qin.

00:05:58.720 --> 00:06:00.840
The route map has been converted to code and sent.

00:06:00.840 --> 00:06:02.320
Received receipt at 8:50.

00:06:02.720 --> 00:06:03.480
The comrades

00:06:03.640 --> 00:06:05.170
have all evacuated safely.

00:06:11.240 --> 00:06:13.500
The radio at the ad agency was destroyed.

00:06:14.120 --> 00:06:16.650
Comrade Lin Heming also sacrificed his life.

00:06:23.960 --> 00:06:25.040
From today on,

00:06:26.960 --> 00:06:28.360
this is the battlefield.

00:06:29.480 --> 00:06:30.940
You two are the main force.

00:06:32.360 --> 00:06:33.690
We will fight together.

00:06:37.159 --> 00:06:37.920
Sister Qin.

00:06:38.560 --> 00:06:40.360
We've been ready for a long time.

00:06:58.600 --> 00:06:59.520
Do you know

00:07:01.360 --> 00:07:02.040
why our telegraphers

00:07:02.040 --> 00:07:03.880
are called by comrades

00:07:06.000 --> 00:07:07.660
'starlight in the night sky'?

00:07:08.280 --> 00:07:09.040
We know.

00:07:09.800 --> 00:07:12.530
Because although there are many stars in the sky,

00:07:13.440 --> 00:07:15.700
most don't shine for more than two years.

00:07:18.720 --> 00:07:21.050
But there will always be new stars rising.

00:07:26.120 --> 00:07:27.400
You have to be the star

00:07:29.520 --> 00:07:31.040
that shines longer.

00:07:33.600 --> 00:07:34.280
Sister.

00:07:35.320 --> 00:07:37.320
We promise to complete the mission.

00:07:52.280 --> 00:07:54.140
You just got married not long ago.

00:07:54.960 --> 00:07:56.120
I haven't had time

00:07:56.960 --> 00:07:58.560
to wish you a happy marriage.

00:07:59.960 --> 00:08:00.890
Happy marriage.

00:08:06.480 --> 00:08:08.140
Thank you, Sister. Thank you.

00:08:08.480 --> 00:08:09.440
Happy marriage.

00:08:24.040 --> 00:08:25.840
Every successful transmission

00:08:27.320 --> 00:08:28.920
involves great danger,

00:08:30.240 --> 00:08:32.440
and requires immeasurable sacrifice.

00:08:41.559 --> 00:08:44.090
This is your last transmission point, right?

00:08:46.440 --> 00:08:47.120
Yes.

00:08:49.600 --> 00:08:50.730
How long do you think

00:08:51.280 --> 00:08:52.680
this place can hold out?

00:08:57.880 --> 00:08:58.640
I don't know.

00:09:02.240 --> 00:09:03.770
If it weren't for Suzuki Ko,

00:09:04.600 --> 00:09:06.600
maybe we could have held out longer.

00:09:12.440 --> 00:09:13.920
Suzuki Ko.

00:09:14.640 --> 00:09:16.520
Do you have any ideas, brother?

00:09:18.960 --> 00:09:20.090
I don't know either.

00:09:22.120 --> 00:09:23.720
If I cast this line,

00:09:25.080 --> 00:09:27.340
I don't know what kind of fish I'll catch.

00:09:41.840 --> 00:09:42.520
Next month,

00:09:42.600 --> 00:09:45.920
Manchukuo is holding a concert in Harbin.

00:09:46.000 --> 00:09:47.460
They need a harmonica band

00:09:47.600 --> 00:09:49.160
to play "Kimigayo"

00:09:49.480 --> 00:09:51.740
and the "National Anthem of Manchukuo".

00:09:52.000 --> 00:09:52.880
I've always

00:09:53.120 --> 00:09:56.040
wanted to enjoy Miss Qin's harmonica performance.

00:09:57.120 --> 00:09:59.920
As long as you agree to lead the band in the performance,

00:09:59.920 --> 00:10:01.000
those children

00:10:01.240 --> 00:10:02.560
can go home right away.

00:10:06.200 --> 00:10:07.080
I'm a person

00:10:08.000 --> 00:10:09.130
who values old ties.

00:10:10.840 --> 00:10:11.800
For the sake of

00:10:12.080 --> 00:10:14.810
my past business relationship with your father,

00:10:16.000 --> 00:10:18.330
I'll give you three days to think about it.

00:10:18.400 --> 00:10:19.160
No need.

00:10:22.640 --> 00:10:23.970
I promise you right now.

00:10:24.480 --> 00:10:25.200
But

00:10:25.760 --> 00:10:27.760
please keep your word, Mr. Matsuda,

00:10:28.920 --> 00:10:30.580
and release the children now.

00:10:34.640 --> 00:10:35.400
Very well.

00:10:36.560 --> 00:10:38.000
I hope to see as soon as possible

00:10:38.000 --> 00:10:39.000
those children

00:10:39.480 --> 00:10:41.520
rehearsing in the harmonica club.

00:10:41.880 --> 00:10:42.640
No problem.

00:10:44.080 --> 00:10:45.200
Those two songs

00:10:45.720 --> 00:10:47.440
are relatively easy to play.

00:10:48.520 --> 00:10:49.880
I hope to give them time

00:10:50.080 --> 00:10:51.280
to heal their wounds.

00:10:55.560 --> 00:10:56.520
Extra.

00:10:56.720 --> 00:10:58.800
Harmonica band captain assassinated,

00:10:58.800 --> 00:11:00.860
famous writer denounces the killer.

00:11:01.200 --> 00:11:02.400
Here, give me a paper.

00:11:08.880 --> 00:11:09.960
Extra.

00:11:10.760 --> 00:11:11.720
Give me one.

00:13:04.080 --> 00:13:06.560
Miss Qin.

00:13:13.000 --> 00:13:14.330
Everyone has suffered.

00:13:17.000 --> 00:13:17.760
Zhou.

00:13:19.720 --> 00:13:21.650
How are your injuries recovering?

00:13:22.480 --> 00:13:23.320
Ms. Qin.

00:13:24.440 --> 00:13:26.440
The physical injuries are nothing,

00:13:27.080 --> 00:13:28.200
but mentally...

00:13:39.240 --> 00:13:40.840
Although Captain Gu is gone,

00:13:41.200 --> 00:13:43.060
the harmonica club is still here.

00:13:44.040 --> 00:13:46.440
Everyone must be ready to leave at any time.

00:13:46.440 --> 00:13:47.200
Leave?

00:13:48.480 --> 00:13:49.400
Where to?

00:13:51.640 --> 00:13:52.640
To the rear area.

00:13:53.680 --> 00:13:55.340
Carry on Captain Gu's legacy.

00:13:55.760 --> 00:13:57.560
Use the harmonicas in your hands

00:13:58.480 --> 00:13:59.920
as a second gun in the resistance against Japan.